divs: Sighting DetailsWe were up high on hill overlooking lake shastina, by MT. Shasta and taking photos of my fathers house that was across the lake with our camera phone. Days later when I went to review the photo's I discovered an unknown object in photo. I am trying to have the photo taken off my camera to have scanned. I beleive if this is to be true maybe the first photo of a ufo that cannot be altered since it is on a camera phone. we have 1 close up photo and one far away photo. Thanks
Summary: caught unknown at time on Camera Phone Photo
